@ENDNODE
@NODE Bugs "Bugs"

@{b}@{fg shine}What works wrong?@{fg text}@{ub}
            
Somebody makes frames around signatures from "-", "_" or "=" chars.
@{b}TruncateMail@{ub} will recognise them as advertisements and remove.

@{b}TruncateMail@{ub} do not works correctly when CONTENT lines in header are
corrupted.
      
TruncateFolder.yam arexx script could not find the folder directory, if path
contains space-char.
 
@ENDNODE
